# Licence-Plate-Generator

This project is inspired by the vast collection of virtual license plates on the SCS Truck World website. By combining cutting-edge 3A technologies, we have built a license plate generation tool.

Inspired by the license plate customization experience on the SCS Software Truck World website, this project aims to bring that immersive sense of personalization to the open-source community. We are **proud** to announce that this is a carefully crafted **AAA-level** open-source project. It is not just a license plate generator, but also a tool that helps advance this **experimental** project.

## Core Features

- Multi-country license plate template library  
- Well-designed UI  
- More features coming soon  
- Custom text input support  

## Technical Architecture

- Frontend Framework: Vanilla JavaScript + HTML5 Canvas with automatic switching to Three.js depending on device capability, ensuring maximum compatibility  
- Styling System: CSS3 variables and modular LESS with dynamic theme switching support  

